If you are more familiar with other technologies, then you may use those if you prefer.  When writing this application, please build it as though it could be the foundation of a much larger application, making it relatively flexible and extensible within your engineering judgement.\
\
Please spend a sensible amount of time of this assignment.  No need to over-engineer it; we primarily want to get a sense of your problem solving approach and software design patterns.\
\
Once you\'92re done working on your prototype, you may share it with us via github.com, or you may email it to us in a zip. Afterward, you should expect to have a few interviews with other members of the team. Please be prepared to discuss your development decisions for your application, and how you might choose to extend the application if you were to put more time into it.\
